lead_paragraph: A Chinese provincial department appeared to have inadvertently confirmed the existence of an intercontinental ballistic missile that may be able to carry several nuclear warheads and travel as far as the United States.

headline.main: Chinese Provincial Agency May Have Confirmed Secret Long-Range Missile
headline.print_headline: Chinese Provincial Agency May Have Confirmed Secret Long-Range Missile
